headline: AI companies want to know how quickly we can bring speed to power: Duke Energy CEO Harry Sideris
summary: Harry Sideris, Duke Energy CEO, joins 'The Exchange' to discuss how the company is helping develop the AI boom, what questions companies are asking Duke Energy and much more.

headline: Duke Energy five-year capital plan could exceed $100B
summary: The company could add more than 13 GW of new capacity to its system over the next five years, CEO Harry Sideris said.
